 winning the [[2006\u201307 Macedonian Football Cup]].\n\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Results ==\nEvery team will play three times against each other team for a total of 33 matches. The first 22 matchdays will consist of a regular double round-robin schedule. The league standings at this point will then be used to determine the games for the last 11 matchdays.\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Matches 1\u201322===\n{{#invoke:sports results|main\n|matches_style=FBR\n|team1=BAS|team2=BRE|team3=MGP|team4=NAP|team5=PEL\n|team6=POB|team7=RAB|team8=REN|team9=SKE|team10=SIL\n|team11=VAR|team12=VLZ\n\n|name_BAS=[[KF Bashkimi (1947\u20132008)|Bashkimi]]\n|match_BAS_BRE=8\u20131\n|match_BAS_MGP=2\u20132\n|match_BAS_NAP=2\u20131\n|match_BAS_PEL=1\u20132\n|match_BAS_POB=2\u20132\n|match_BAS_RAB=1\u20133\n|match_BAS_REN=0\u20133\n|match_BAS_SKE=6\u20131\n|match_BAS_SIL=1\u20130\n|match_BAS_VAR=0\u20133\n|match_BAS_VLZ=2\u20130\n\n|name_BRE=[[FK Bregalnica \u0160tip|Bregalnica Kraun]]\n|match_BRE_BAS=0\u20135\n|match_BRE_MGP=2\u20133\n|match_BRE_NAP=1\u20132\n|match_BRE_PEL=0\u20134\n|match_BRE_POB=1\u20131\n|match_BRE_RAB=0\u20133\n|match_BRE_REN=1\u20130\n|match_BRE_SKE=0\u20133\n|match_BRE_SIL=0\u20132\n|match_BRE_VAR=0\u20133\n|match_BRE_VLZ=5\u20131\n\n|name_MGP=[[FK Makedonija Gjor\u010de Petrov|Makedonija]]\n|match_MGP_BAS=1\u20131\n|match_MGP_BRE=3\u20130\n|match_MGP_NAP=2\u20131\n|match_MGP_PEL=2\u20130\n|match_MGP_POB=0\u20130\n|match_MGP_RAB=3\u20130\n|match_MGP_REN=1\u20131\n|match_MGP_SKE=2\u20130\n|match_MGP_SIL=3\u20131\n|match_MGP_VAR=0\u20132\n|match_MGP_VLZ=3\u20130\n\n|name_NAP=[[FK Napredok|Napredok]]\n|match_NAP_BAS=1\u20130\n|match_NAP_BRE=7\u20130\n|match_NAP_MGP=1\u20130\n|match_NAP_PEL=0\u20130\n|match_NAP_POB=2\u20132\n|match_NAP_RAB=0\u20130\n|match_NAP_REN=1\u20131\n|match_NAP_SKE=2\u20132\n|match_NAP_SIL=2\u20130\n|match_NAP_VAR=1\u20133\n|match_NAP_VLZ=3\u20130\n\n|name_PEL=[[FK Pelister|Pelister]]\n|match_PEL_BAS=2\u20130\n|match_PEL_BRE=3\u20130\n|match